.TH hldigconfig 8 "2018-04-04"
.\" NAME should be all caps, SECTION should be 1-8, maybe w/ subsection
.\" other parms are allowed: see man(7), man(1)
.SH NAME
hldigconfig \- script to create fuzzy databases for hl://Dig
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hldigconfig
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.I hldigconfig
is a script to create fuzzy databases such as word2root, root2word and 
synonyms databases for the hl://Dig search engine.
.SH "SEE ALSO"
Please refer to the HTML pages (in the hldig-doc package)
.B /usr/share/doc/hldig/html/index.html
for a detailed description of hl://Dig and its commands.
.SH AUTHOR
